# RetroWeather 3000 — Environment Variables

This project uses the **keyless [Open-Meteo API](https://open-meteo.com/)** and requires **no environment variables** to run.

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

If you deploy to Vercel or another platform, you do not need to configure any secrets.

Optional: copy this file to `.env.local` if you want to document local overrides in the future — none are required today.
